description.en: Digital Financial Exchange token (DIFX) is the native token associated with the cryptocurrency exchange DIFX. Based on the Ethereum/Binance Smart Chain blockchain, this digital asset is ERC-20/BEP-20 compliant and decentralized. DIFX's value is dependent in part on the reputation of its crypto exchange.
